&lt;p&gt;Today, OONI is thrilled to announce the public launch of the &lt;strong&gt;new OONI
Probe desktop app&lt;/strong&gt; that you can download and install on &lt;strong&gt;Windows&lt;/strong&gt; and
&lt;strong&gt;macOS&lt;/strong&gt; to measure internet censorship and network performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a class="ooni-btn" href="https://ooni.org/install/desktop"&gt;Install OONI Probe Desktop app&lt;/a&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By running the tests in the new OONI Probe desktop app, you can measure:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Blocking of &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/web-connectivity/"&gt;websites&lt;/a&gt;;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Blocking of &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/whatsapp/"&gt;WhatsApp&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/facebook-messenger/"&gt;Facebook Messenger&lt;/a&gt;, and
&lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/telegram/"&gt;Telegram&lt;/a&gt;;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Blocking of &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/tor/"&gt;Tor&lt;/a&gt; and
&lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/psiphon/"&gt;Psiphon&lt;/a&gt;;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Presence of systems (“&lt;a href="https://ooni.org/nettest/http-invalid-request-line/"&gt;middleboxes&lt;/a&gt;”)
that could potentially be responsible for censorship and/or surveillance;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>New OONI Probe Mobile App: Measure Internet Censorship &amp; Performance</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/post/ooni-mobile-app/</link><pubDate>Thu, 09 Feb 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/post/ooni-mobile-app/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://ooni.github.io/post/ooni-mobile-app/ooni-mobile-app.jpg" alt="OONI mobile app"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
