announce the release of a new mobile app (“&lt;strong&gt;OONI Probe - Measure Internet
Censorship &amp;amp; Performance&lt;/strong&gt;”) that can now be installed on &lt;strong&gt;Android&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;iOS&lt;/strong&gt; for
testing Internet censorship and network performance.&lt;/p&gt;
